snippet.title: Pushpa 2 Movie REVIEW | Deeksha Sharma
snippet.description:
Pushpa 2 Movie Review In Hindi By Deeksha Sharma. Pushpa 2 The Rule Featuring Allu Arjun & Rashmika Mandanna with Fahadh Faasil Directed by Sukumar is the Most Awaited Sequel to Pushpa 2021 Film with Big Budget New Enemies & Dark Twist in the Special Climax to beat Baahubali to become the No.1 Indian Film at Box Office. Pushpa 2 Full Movie Story Outline Explained & Positives Negatives would be shared in this Video. Can Allu Arjun Pushpa 2 beat Prabhas & Rajamouli Records to change the Pan India Game Forever- Find out inside!

snippet.title: PEELINGS (Telugu Lyrical Video) | Pushpa 2 The Rule | Allu Arjun | Rashmika Mandanna | Sukumar | DSP
snippet.description:
The Most Loved Jodi is Coming🔥! The Icon Star 'Allu Arjun' & the Amazing 'Rashmika Mandanna' is Ready to Set the Stage on fire with this New Banger!

Pushpa 2 - The Rule - Written and Directed by Sukumar. Produced by Naveen Yerneni and Y. Ravi Shankar of Mythri Movie Makers in association with Sukumar Writings. The film stars Allu Arjun, Fahadh Faasil, Rashmika Mandanna, Dhanunjay, Rao Ramesh, Sunil, Anasuya Bharadwaj & Ajay Ghosh. The film's music is composed by Devi Sri Prasad, with cinematography and editing performed by Miroslaw Kuba Brozek and Navin Nooli respectively.

Releasing in Cinemas on 5th December 2024💥😍🔥!

As per the latest reports, Pushpa 2: The Rule has broken several box office records, including the highest opening day collection for a Telugu film. The film is All Set To gross over ₹250+ crores on its opening day, surpassing the records of several other big-budget films.

The film's success can be attributed to its engaging storyline, impressive performances, and outstanding direction. Allu Arjun, who plays the lead role of Pushpa Raj, has delivered a power-packed performance, which has been widely appreciated by the audience.

Rashmika Mandana, who plays the role of Srivalli, has also delivered a impressive performance, and her chemistry with Allu Arjun has been widely praised. Fahadh Faasil, who plays the role of the main antagonist, has also delivered a memorable performance.

The film's music, composed by Devi Sri Prasad, has also been widely appreciated, with several songs becoming chartbusters. The film's cinematography, handled by Miroslaw Kuba Brozek, has also been praised for its outstanding visuals.

Overall, Pushpa 2: The Rule is a must-watch film for all movie lovers. With its engaging storyline, impressive performances, and outstanding direction, the film is sure to entertain audiences of all ages.

snippet.title: Gukesh vs Ding Liren | Game 7 | FIDE World Championship 2024 | Ft. Sagar, Tania, Biswa, Balraj
snippet.description:
Watch it LIVE in person in Habitat in Mumbai: https://in.bookmyshow.com/sports/world-chess-championship-broadcast-2024-gukesh-v-ding-liren/ET00420952

The FIDE World Championship 2024 match is the first in 138 years to feature two contestants from Asia, the reigning World Champion, China’s Ding Liren and challenger Dommaraju Gukesh from India competing for the title and a prize fund of US$2.5 million.

The schedule of the World Championship match takes place over 3 weeks, with 14 match days and 4 rest days planned. All games start at 17:00 local time (2.30 p.m. IST) and there are rest days after Games 3, 6, 9 and 12. The first player to reach 7.5 points will be the winner; in the case of a tie after 14 games, tiebreaks will be played the next day to decide the winner.

Pushpa Raj is back with a bang, and the anticipation is sky high for Pushpa2: The Rule as the premiere show unfolds, fans are eager to witness the action-packed drama and Allu arjun's charismatic return. From the intense visuals to the powerful performance, this film promises to set new benchmarks. With Sukumar's brilliant direction and Devi Sri Prasad's pulsating music, Pushpa2 is a cinematic spectacle in the making. Join me Ravi Telugu Traveller, as I bring you the first review of this much awaited sequel.

Pushpa 2: The Rule undoubtedly delivers a high-octane experience, living up to the hype and expectations. Allu Arjun shines in every frame, embodying the rugged charm of Pushpa Raj with finesse, while the gripping narrative keeps you hooked. Sukumar's storytelling elevates the action drama genre,blending raw emotions with larger-than-life moments.The music,visuals,and performances come together seamlessly,creating an unforgettable cinematic experience.If you're a fan of intense action,gripping drama,and a powerful storyline,Pushpa 2 is a must Watch Movie.

snippet.title: 🔴 Rain Alert : బంగాళాఖాతంలో మరో అల్పపీడనం.. - TV9
snippet.description:
ఎక్కడో నైరుతి బంగాళాఖాతంలో తమిళనాడుకు దగ్గరలో ఏర్పడింది... పుదుచ్చేరి దగ్గర తీరం దాటింది... కానీ దాని ప్రభావం మాత్రం దాదాపు 1,500 కిలో మీటర్ల దూరంలో ఉన్న ఒడిశాపైనా చూపించింది. ఇదీ...  ఫెయింజల్‌ తుపాను విరుచుకుపడిన తీరు. తుపానుగా మారిన కొద్ది సేపటికే బలహీనపడటం.. మళ్లీ తుపానుగా మారడం.. ఇలా భిన్న రూపాలతో  ఫెయింజల్‌ ఇబ్బంది పెట్టింది. నవంబర్‌ 30వ తేదీ ఉదయం 8 గంటలకు నైరుతి బంగాళాఖాతం నుంచి చెన్నై వైపుగా కదిలింది.

snippet.title: Jetha और Bhide ने उठाए 5 Variety के खाने के मज़े! | Taarak Mehta Ka Ooltah Chashmah Ke Foodies
snippet.description:
Click here to Subscribe to LIV Comedy: 
https://www.youtube.com/channel/UCBIT1FSJW6yTlzqK-31FDWg?sub_confirmation=1

Daya, Madhavi, Komal, Anjali and Babita bring tiffins at Sodhi's place one by one. Bhide thinks that the "Ganesh Utsav" is approaching and Tapu Sena hasn't come to him yet, so he decides to go to Tapu Sena and ask about the "Ganesh Utsav" program.

Show Name - Taarak Mehta Ka Ooltah Chashmah
Star Cast - Dilip Joshi, Disha Vakani, Amit Bhatt
Episode - 685
Produced By - Asit Kumar Modi, Neela Asit Modi

#taarakmehtakaooltahchashmah #livcomedy #tmkoc #comedy2024 #तारकमेहताकाउल्टाचश्मा #comedy #jethalal #tarakmehta #jethalalmemes #tmkocmemes #jethalalcomedy #food #foodies #foodie #gokuldham #fullepisode #comedyvideos #foodlover 
 
About The Show:
----------------------------
Taarak Mehta Ka Ooltah Chashmah is a comedy show inspired by the famous humorous column 'Duniya Ne Undha Chashmah' written by the eminent Gujarati writer Mr. Tarak Mehta. This show revolves around the Gada Family which consists of uneducated businessmen Jethalal Champaklal Gada, Jethalal’s Wife Daya & their naughty Son Tipendra Gada living in Gokuldham Co-operative Society' and covers topical issues which are socially relevant. In case of a problem and emergency, Jethalal Gada often rushes to Taarak Mehta to seek his help and guidance as he finds a philosopher in him. The housing society residents help each other find solutions when facing common, real-life challenges and getting involved in sticky situations.

Click here to watch more episodes from 'Taarak Mehta Ka Ooltah Chashmah Ke Foodies' : https://www.youtube.com/playlist?list=PLSXTaG1fT0cT5G12J5Crvkt1XPr2dP5iG

7th Sky Entertainment’s highly anticipated mega signature project, Sunn Mere Dil, is the most awaited drama serial. The mega drama boasts a star-studded cast led by Wahaj Ali and Maya Ali. Written by the renowned Khalil Ur Rehman Qamar and directed by the acclaimed Haseeb Hasan, Sunn Mere Dil promises to be a one-of-a-kind drama.

Sunn Mere Dil is a tale in which love finds a new meaning, where one person’s devotion quietly flourishes, often unnoticed. Their heart beats for someone who may never truly understand the depth of their feelings. Yet, in their silent sacrifices, they realize that true love is not about
possession but about selflessness.

Every unspoken gesture and unseen act of kindness brings them fulfillment, as they put their beloved’s happiness above their own, showing that love is not just about being together, it’s about redefining happiness, even at the expense of their contentment.

snippet.title: Jetha ने लिए Pav Bhaji & Pani Puri खाखरा के मज़े | Taarak Mehta Ka Ooltah Chashmah Ke Foodies
snippet.description:
Click here to Subscribe to LIV Comedy: 
https://www.youtube.com/channel/UCBIT1FSJW6yTlzqK-31FDWg?sub_confirmation=1

The breakfast that their wives have prepared for them has left the men of the society feeling let down. The primary victims, Taarak and Jetha, are depressed because one puts uninteresting food on the table and the other postpones breakfast. To learn more, watch the entire episode.

Show Name - Taarak Mehta Ka Ooltah Chashmah
Star Cast - Dilip Joshi, Disha Vakani, Amit Bhatt
Episode - 485
Produced By - Asit Kumar Modi, Neela Asit Modi

#taarakmehtakaooltahchashmah #livcomedy #tmkoc #comedy2024 #तारकमेहताकाउल्टाचश्मा #comedy #jethalal #tarakmehta #jethalalmemes #tmkocmemes #jethalalcomedy #food #foodies #foodie #gokuldham #fullepisode #comedyvideos #foodlover 
 
About The Show:
----------------------------
Taarak Mehta Ka Ooltah Chashmah is a comedy show inspired by the famous humorous column 'Duniya Ne Undha Chashmah' written by the eminent Gujarati writer Mr. Tarak Mehta. This show revolves around the Gada Family which consists of uneducated businessmen Jethalal Champaklal Gada, Jethalal’s Wife Daya & their naughty Son Tipendra Gada living in Gokuldham Co-operative Society' and covers topical issues which are socially relevant. In case of a problem and emergency, Jethalal Gada often rushes to Taarak Mehta to seek his help and guidance as he finds a philosopher in him. The housing society residents help each other find solutions when facing common, real-life challenges and getting involved in sticky situations.

Click here to watch more episodes from 'Taarak Mehta Ka Ooltah Chashmah Ke Foodies' : https://www.youtube.com/playlist?list=PLSXTaG1fT0cT5G12J5Crvkt1XPr2dP5iG

About the show: 
----------------------------------------------------------------------
Taarak Mehta Ka Ooltah Chashmah is a SAB Comedy Show inspired by the famous humorous column, Duniya Ne Undha Chashmah written by the eminent Gujarati writer, Mr. Tarak Mehta. This show revolves around the Gada family which consists of businessman, Jethalal Champaklal Gada, Jethalal's wife, Daya & their naughty son, Tipendra Gada living in Gokuldham Co-operative Society, and covers topical issues that are socially relevant. This hilarious show will surely tickle your funny bone.

This show revolves around the Gada family which consists of businessman, Jethalal Champaklal Gada, Jethalal's wife, Daya & their naughty son, Tipendra Gada living in Gokuldham Co-operative Society, and covers topical issues that are socially relevant. This hilarious show will surely tickle your funny bone.

Lyrics - 

1
नौकरानी बना के रखल तू रानी के सपना देखाके 
ओला बोलाके चलनी हम ए राजा जी माइके 
पहिले जे जनती चूल्हा चौकी करवइबा 
नदिया किनार भेजी पानी भरवइबs 
त कबो ना बियाहवा रचइती आहो राजा 
माँगे ना सेनुरा टिकवइती 
आहो राजा कबो ना बियाहवा रचइती 

              antra 
हई साड़ी दिहल पापा जी के 
गाड़ी दिहल पापा जी के 
जवना पर घूमी तू ऐस करेलs 
कबहुँ खरच नाही कैश करेलs 

2.
कूल्ही कमइया सवत पर उरईब 
सारी सारी रात पिया ओनिए बितइब 
त आपन भोजन ना बसियइती 
आहो राजा मांगे ना सेनुरा टिकइति 

          antra 
कूलर फ्रीज़ पंखा टीवी 
संघे पइला सुनर बीवी 
तबो काहे ना पिया कदर करेल
हर घड़ी हमसे ग़दर करेल

3
जनती ना पवन पिया एतना सतइबा 
मेकअप सेकअप खातिर एतना रोवइब 
त प्रिंस ले ऑर्डर करवईती 
आहो राजा मांगे ना सेनुरा टिकवइती 
आहो राजा कबो ना बियाहवा रचइती

#LakshmiBaramma #Drama #ColorsKannada #KannadaSerials

snippet.title: The smartphone from 2040 just arrived today...
snippet.description:
There are no camera bumps in the future! Current pricing of the Red Magic 10 Pro is here: https://bit.ly/3YUsbDV Gaming phones are where new technology usually comes to light for the first time. And this Red Magic 10 Pro with a built in 23,000rm turbo fan active cooling system is no different. With a freakin' sweet under screen camera, and a liquid metal cooling system (which we will see during the teardown) I'm excited for the smartphones of the future! 

If this is what the future of smartphones look like - im here for it! 

Red Magic provided these 2 phones for my review - all opinions are my own. To win the non-damaged Dusk Red Magic 10 Pro in this video just leave any comment on this video - and Ill pick 1 (one) Random winner in the next 7 days. The winner will be notified publicly with a response on their comment from my verified YouTube channel.

Kraven the Hunter is the visceral, action-packed origin story of how and why one of Marvel's most iconic villains came to be. Aaron Taylor-Johnson plays Kraven, a man whose complex relationship with his ruthless father, Nikolai Kravinoff (Russell Crowe), starts him down a path of vengeance with brutal consequences, motivating him to become not only the greatest hunter in the world, but also one of its most feared. 

Directed by: J.C. Chandor

Story by: Richard Wenk

Screenplay by: Richard Wenk and Art Marcum & Matt Holloway

Based on the Marvel Comics

Avi Arad

David Householter

Cast:

snippet.title: Sukhbir Badal 'ਤੇ ਹਮਲੇ ਦੀ ਕੋਸ਼ਿਸ਼ ਤੋਂ ਬਾਅਦ Bhagwant Mann ਨੇ ਕੀ ਕਿਹਾ | 𝐁𝐁𝐂 𝐏𝐔𝐍𝐉𝐀𝐁𝐈
snippet.description:
ਸੁਖਬੀਰ ਬਾਦਲ ਉੱਤੇ ਹਮਲੇ ਦੀ ਕੋਸ਼ਿਸ਼ ਤੋਂ ਬਾਅਦ ਇਸ ਘਟਨਾ 'ਤੇ ਸਿਆਸੀ ਅਤੇ ਧਾਰਮਿਕ ਆਗੂਆਂ ਵੱਲੋਂ ਪ੍ਰਤੀਕਿਰਿਆਵਾਂ ਦਾ ਦੌਰ ਵੀ ਜਾਰੀ ਹੈ। ਸ੍ਰੀ ਅਕਾਲ ਤਖਤ ਸਾਹਿਬ ਦੇ ਜਥੇਦਾਰ ਗਿਆਨੀ ਰਘਬੀਰ ਸਿੰਘ ਨੇ ਇਸ ਘਟਨਾ ਤੋਂ ਬਾਅਦ ਸਰਕਾਰ ਨੂੰ ਤਾੜਨਾ ਕੀਤੀ ਹੈ। ਅਕਾਲੀ ਆਗੂਆਂ ਸਣੇ ਬੀਜੇਪੀ ਅਤੇ ਕਾਂਗਰਸ ਨੇ ਵੀ ਸਵਾਲ ਖੜੇ ਕੀਤੇ ਹਨ। ਮੁੱਖ ਮੰਤਰੀ ਨੇ ਵੀ ਇਨ੍ਹਾਂ ਇਲਜ਼ਾਮਾਂ ਉੱਤੇ ਜਵਾਬ ਦਿੱਤਾ ਹੈ , ਕੌਣ ਕੀ ਬੋਲਿਆ ਹੈ ਜਾਣਦੇ ਹਾਂ ਇਸ ਰਿਪੋਰਟ ਵਿੱਚ..
ਵੀਡੀਓ:ਰਵਿੰਦਰ ਸਿੰਘ ਰੌਬਿਨ, ਐਡਿਟ:ਰਾਜਨ ਪਪਨੇਜਾ

localized.title: Sukhbir Badal 'ਤੇ ਹਮਲੇ ਦੀ ਕੋਸ਼ਿਸ਼ ਤੋਂ ਬਾਅਦ Bhagwant Mann ਨੇ ਕੀ ਕਿਹਾ | 𝐁𝐁𝐂 𝐏𝐔𝐍𝐉𝐀𝐁𝐈
localized.description:
ਸੁਖਬੀਰ ਬਾਦਲ ਉੱਤੇ ਹਮਲੇ ਦੀ ਕੋਸ਼ਿਸ਼ ਤੋਂ ਬਾਅਦ ਇਸ ਘਟਨਾ 'ਤੇ ਸਿਆਸੀ ਅਤੇ ਧਾਰਮਿਕ ਆਗੂਆਂ ਵੱਲੋਂ ਪ੍ਰਤੀਕਿਰਿਆਵਾਂ ਦਾ ਦੌਰ ਵੀ ਜਾਰੀ ਹੈ। ਸ੍ਰੀ ਅਕਾਲ ਤਖਤ ਸਾਹਿਬ ਦੇ ਜਥੇਦਾਰ ਗਿਆਨੀ ਰਘਬੀਰ ਸਿੰਘ ਨੇ ਇਸ ਘਟਨਾ ਤੋਂ ਬਾਅਦ ਸਰਕਾਰ ਨੂੰ ਤਾੜਨਾ ਕੀਤੀ ਹੈ। ਅਕਾਲੀ ਆਗੂਆਂ ਸਣੇ ਬੀਜੇਪੀ ਅਤੇ ਕਾਂਗਰਸ ਨੇ ਵੀ ਸਵਾਲ ਖੜੇ ਕੀਤੇ ਹਨ। ਮੁੱਖ ਮੰਤਰੀ ਨੇ ਵੀ ਇਨ੍ਹਾਂ ਇਲਜ਼ਾਮਾਂ ਉੱਤੇ ਜਵਾਬ ਦਿੱਤਾ ਹੈ , ਕੌਣ ਕੀ ਬੋਲਿਆ ਹੈ ਜਾਣਦੇ ਹਾਂ ਇਸ ਰਿਪੋਰਟ ਵਿੱਚ..
ਵੀਡੀਓ:ਰਵਿੰਦਰ ਸਿੰਘ ਰੌਬਿਨ, ਐਡਿਟ:ਰਾਜਨ ਪਪਨੇਜਾ
#sukhbirsinghbadal #amritsar #punjab

Episode 4257: Sodhi's Party Plans
--------------------------------------------------------
With his friend coming from Punjab, Sodhi is set to celebrate his birthday in style. But will Roshan let him party?

Show Name – Taarak Mehta Ka Ooltah Chashmah
Star Cast –  Dilip Joshi, Disha Vakani, Amit Bhatt, Nitish Bhaluni

#TaarakMehtaKaOoltahChashmah #तारकमेहताकाउल्टाचश्मा #sab #Latest #New #TaarakMehtaKaOoltahChashmah2024 #tmkocfunnyepisodes #hindicomedy #comedyvideo #16yearsoftmkoc  #4000episodes

About the show: 
----------------------------------------------------------------------
Taarak Mehta Ka Ooltah Chashmah is a SAB Comedy Show inspired by the famous humorous column, Duniya Ne Undha Chashmah written by the eminent Gujarati writer, Mr. Tarak Mehta. This show revolves around the Gada family which consists of businessman, Jethalal Champaklal Gada, Jethalal's wife, Daya & their naughty son, Tipendra Gada living in Gokuldham Co-operative Society, and covers topical issues that are socially relevant. This hilarious show will surely tickle your funny bone.

About the show: 
----------------------------------------------------------------------
Taarak Mehta Ka Ooltah Chashmah is a SAB Comedy Show inspired by the famous humorous column, Duniya Ne Undha Chashmah written by the eminent Gujarati writer, Mr. Tarak Mehta. This show revolves around the Gada family which consists of businessman, Jethalal Champaklal Gada, Jethalal's wife, Daya & their naughty son, Tipendra Gada living in Gokuldham Co-operative Society, and covers topical issues that are socially relevant. This hilarious show will surely tickle your funny bone.

snippet.description:

Download App - https://go.jc.fm/fRhd/ltxxrhby

Facebook - https://www.facebook.com/share/r/WaXaTdYV9VSP3JVU/?mibextid=hBBs4f

Gayatri लगी Lakshmi का घर उजाड़ने में

 Watch more viodes from the show here: https://www.youtube.com/playlist?list=PLdMXQl51UbMjX6BwpnuG6rvMN9N77mtRg

-----
Mangal Lakshmi unfolds as a poignant narrative, delving into the profound connection shared between two sisters, Mangal and Lakshmi. Set against life's myriad experiences, the story chronicles Mangal's odyssey in search of the ideal match, a 'dulha', for her cherished sibling, Lakshmi. As the tale progresses, it gracefully illustrates the intricacies of love, the resilience required to overcome trials, and the unwavering resolve that propels Mangal forward on her quest. Through the lens of sisterhood's enduring bond and the inexorable force of destiny, the narrative unfurls a tapestry of emotions, ultimately celebrating the timeless allure of fate in uniting kindred spirits.

Star Cast: Deepika Singh, Shubham Dipta, Naman Shaw, Upadhyay Urvashi,Vipul Tyagi

snippet.title: BISCUITS HALWA | Delicious Biscuit Recipe Cooking in Village | Sweet Halwa Recipe using Biscuits
snippet.description:
Today, in our village, we cook a halwa recipe using biscuits. Usually, halwa is made with wheat flour, but we use biscuits instead of any flour. This is a very easy snack recipe that everyone can easily cook in minutes.

We add milk, palm jaggery, and some nuts to make the halwa tastier and more traditional.

We taste the warm halwa on a rainy day evening! 

The taste is Delicious!
